platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Bookend your days with a moment of reflection in stoic., an elegantly designed journaling app made for anyone looking to carve out time for mindfulness. With insightful reflection prompts and breathing exercises, the app is filled with multiple ways to care for your mental health—with inspiration from stoic philosophy at its core.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Meet your daily companion for journaling, meditation and reflection.
